            <li>Batch processing or long-running jobs (up to 15 min)</li>
            <li>Multi-language requirements</li>
            <li>Complex compute-intensive work</li>
            <li>Organizations already standardized on AWS</li>
            <li>Specific IAM security requirements</li>
            <li>Integration with Lambda@Edge or CloudFront</li>
            <li>VPC networking requirements</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
